Instructions for galaxy installation on a Server.

This is the link for settin up galaxy on a production server.
http://wiki.g2.bx.psu.edu/Admin/Config/Performance/Production%20Server

Required tools for install commands for installation on a linux install with
apt-get.

#commands

#install samtools genomics suite
sudo apt-get install samtools

#install tabix tabdelimiter file indexer
sudo apt-get install tabix


sudo apt-get install blast2